{"tid":2298474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"估唔到傑斯單嘢連美國國務院都出聲","createTime":"2020-11-24T05:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T06:09:51.000Z","uid":7369,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"970f7cc6297baecf73633c464e9eb48f70e4dcf3","tid":2298474,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"網台 D100 Radio 主持人傑斯（尹耀昇）、其妻曾碧雲及助手利寶麗日前被警務處國安處拘捕，由傑斯發起的「千個爸媽，台灣助學」計劃被指涉嫌洗黑錢及資助分裂國家。美國國務院發聲明關注，指事件是中共及其香港代理人侵蝕香港人權與新聞自由的又一事例。<br />\n美國國務院副發言人 Cale Brown 表示，美國高度關注香港記者尹耀昇、其妻子、助手等三人被控國安法相關罪名的事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/d100-%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81%E5%82%91%E6%96%AF%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%B4%97%E9%BB%91%E9%8C%A2-%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%99%E9%99%A2%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%B1%E4%BE%B5%E8%9D%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%8F%88%E4%B8%80%E4%BE%8B/?fbclid=IwAR0HiPLfvQSPozLZedGHqst0I6o3-oN6SGOCyClGsMMJDqtqp8uomG1gmZU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fd100-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%25B0%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2582%2591%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%258C%25A2-%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2599%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25B1%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E8%259D%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%258F%2588%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BE%258B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0HiPLfvQSPozLZedGHqst0I6o3-oN6SGOCyClGsMMJDqtqp8uomG1gmZU&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=92fbe459\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fd100-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%25B0%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2582%2591%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B4%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%258C%25A2-%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%258A%25A9%25E